OSEHRA ZGO Export: CUSTOMER SERVICE STANDARDS
ZWR
^QA(745.6,0)="CUSTOMER SERVICE STANDARDS^745.6I^17^17"
^QA(745.6,1,0)="1^Staff Courtesy"
^QA(745.6,1,1,0)="^^2^2^2970804^"
^QA(745.6,1,1,1,0)="We will treat you with courtesy and dignity.  You can expect to be"
^QA(745.6,1,1,2,0)="treated as the 1st class citizen that you are."
^QA(745.6,2,0)="2^Access/Timeliness"
^QA(745.6,2,1,0)="^^3^3^2970804^"
^QA(745.6,2,1,1,0)="We will provide you with timely access to health care.  When you do "
^QA(745.6,2,1,2,0)="have to wait, we will explain why, and we will continually work"
^QA(745.6,2,1,3,0)="to improve."
^QA(745.6,3,0)="3^One Provider"
^QA(745.6,3,1,0)="^^5^5^2970804^"
^QA(745.6,3,1,1,0)="One health care provider will be in charge of your care."
^QA(745.6,3,1,2,0)="Because health care often involves many different providers"
^QA(745.6,3,1,3,0)="it is important that one provider or team have overall "
^QA(745.6,3,1,4,0)="responsibility.  You can expect to know who to contact when "
^QA(745.6,3,1,5,0)="you need help or have a problem."
^QA(745.6,4,0)="4^Decisions/Preferences"
^QA(745.6,4,1,0)="^745.62^4^4^3020322^^^"
^QA(745.6,4,1,1,0)="We will involve you in decisions about your health care as"
^QA(745.6,4,1,2,0)="much you want.  Your preferences for care will be met whenever"
^QA(745.6,4,1,3,0)="possible.  We will listen to your concerns and discuss them"
^QA(745.6,4,1,4,0)="with you."
^QA(745.6,5,0)="5^Emotional Needs"
^QA(745.6,5,1,0)="^^5^5^2970804^"
^QA(745.6,5,1,1,0)="We will provide support to meet your emotional needs.  We will"
^QA(745.6,5,1,2,0)="encourage you to share any anxieties and fears you may have"
^QA(745.6,5,1,3,0)="about your condition or treatment.  You can expect our staff to "
^QA(745.6,5,1,4,0)="be sensitive to your feelings and help you deal with your health "
^QA(745.6,5,1,5,0)="care experience."
^QA(745.6,6,0)="6^Coordination of Care"
^QA(745.6,6,1,0)="^^7^7^2970804^"
^QA(745.6,6,1,1,0)="We will take responsibility for coordinating your care.  Health"
^QA(745.6,6,1,2,0)="care can be very complicated, and many patients need to see more "
^QA(745.6,6,1,3,0)="than one health care professional.  We will ensure that all your"
^QA(745.6,6,1,4,0)="providers talk with each other and give you clear plans for your"
^QA(745.6,6,1,5,0)="care.  If you need a specialist, you can expect us to make all "
^QA(745.6,6,1,6,0)="arrangements to ensure that you are seen by the necessary"
^QA(745.6,6,1,7,0)="provider."
^QA(745.6,7,0)="7^Patient Education"
^QA(745.6,7,1,0)="^^3^3^2970804^"
^QA(745.6,7,1,1,0)="We will provide information and education about your health care"
^QA(745.6,7,1,2,0)="that you will understand.  You can also expect to have all your"
^QA(745.6,7,1,3,0)="questions answered in a way that you will understand."
^QA(745.6,8,0)="8^Family Involvement"
^QA(745.6,8,1,0)="^^2^2^2970804^"
^QA(745.6,8,1,1,0)="We will provide opportunities to involve your family in your"
^QA(745.6,8,1,2,0)="care.  Whether your family is involved, however, is your choice."
^QA(745.6,9,0)="9^Physical Comfort"
^QA(745.6,9,1,0)="^^5^5^2970804^^"
^QA(745.6,9,1,1,0)="We will strive to meet your physical comfort needs.  This includes"
^QA(745.6,9,1,2,0)="help with things like pain management, eating, bathing, or getting"
^QA(745.6,9,1,3,0)="to the bathroom while in the hospital.  It also includes maintaining"
^QA(745.6,9,1,4,0)="privacy during examinations and tests when an inpatient or outpatient."
^QA(745.6,9,1,5,0)="We will ensure proper facilities for veterans with special needs."
^QA(745.6,10,0)="10^Transitions"
^QA(745.6,10,1,0)="^^6^6^2970804^"
^QA(745.6,10,1,1,0)="We will provide smooth transition between your inpatient and"
^QA(745.6,10,1,2,0)="outpatient care.  You can expect to understand what medicines"
^QA(745.6,10,1,3,0)="you are to take, what danger signals to look out for, and what"
^QA(745.6,10,1,4,0)="activity level you can have after discharge.  You can expect"
^QA(745.6,10,1,5,0)="to know who to contact if you need help or advice right away,"
^QA(745.6,10,1,6,0)="and when your first follow-up appointment is."
